f27%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EApple%20has%20six%20months%20to%20ensure%20compliance.%3Cp%3EPeter%20Macdiarmid%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20EU%20has%20given%C2%A0%20Apple%20six%20months%20to%20ensure%20its%20iPadOS%20complies%20with%20the%20Digital%20Markets%20Act.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20European%20Commission%20said%20users%20are%C2%A0%26quot%3Blocked%20in%26quot%3B%C2%A0to%20iPadOS%20and%20it's%20hard%20for%20them%20to%20switch.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20comes%20as%20a%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20crackdown%20on%20%26quot%3Bgatekeepers%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20market%20investigation%20into%20Apple.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20a%20new%20headache%20to%20deal%20with%20in%20the%20EU.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20European%20Commission%20on%20Monday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fec.europa.eu%2Fcommission%2Fpresscorner%2Fdetail%2Fen%2Fip_24_2363%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eput%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20tech%20giant%20on%20notice%20to%20ensure%20its%20iPad%20operating%20system%20adheres%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa-new-eu-law-targeting-big-tech-could-boost-advertisers-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDigital%20markets%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%20rules%20within%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DMA%20was%20designed%20to%20ensure%20fairness%20and%20healthy%20competition%20in%20the%20digital%20landscape%20and%20hold%20Big%20Tech%20%26quot%3Bgatekeepers%26quot%3B%20accountable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20believes%20that%20one%20way%20of%20doing%20so%20is%20by%20probing%20Apple's%20iPadOS%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20the%20DMA.%20Apple%20has%20its%20work%20cut%20out%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20changes%20it%20will%20have%20to%20make%20to%20become%20compliant%20with%20its%20rules%20include%20letting%20iPad%20users%20remove%20apps%20that%20came%20pre-installed%20on%20the%20device%20and%20allowing%20them%20to%20download%20apps%20from%20other%20app%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20comes%20amid%20a%20broader%20crackdown%20on%20companies%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fec.europa.eu%2Fcommission%2Fpresscorner%2Fdetail%2Fen%2Fip_23_4328%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEU%20describes%20as%20gatekeepers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20follows%20the%20commission's%20decision%20to%20open%20a%20market%20investigation%20in%20September%20to%20review%20whether%20Apple's%20iPadOS%20meets%20its%20DMA%20requirements%2C%20which%20came%20into%20effect%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20the%20EU%20Commission%20designated%20Alphabet%2C%20Amazon%2C%20Apple%2C%20ByteDance%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20Microsoft%20gatekeepers.%20This%20was%20determined%20based%20on%20several%20factors%2C%20including%20their%20economic%20position%2C%20how%20they%20act%20as%20intermediaries%2C%20and%20their%20long-maintained%20dominant%20positions%20in%20their%20respective%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20EU%20said%20Monday%20that%20its%20iPadOS%20investigation%20found%20it%20has%20%26quot%3Bfeatures%20of%20a%20gatekeeper.%26quot%3B%20It%20said%20the%20number%20of%20Apple's%20business%20users%20is%20close%20to%20the%20threshold%20and%20that%20they%20are%20%26quot%3Blocked%20in%26quot%3B%20to%20iPadOS%20as%20the%20firm%20disincentivizes%20users%20from%20switching%20to%20other%20tablets'%20operating%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMargrethe%20Vestager%2C%20who%20leads%20competition%20policy%20at%20the%20commission%2C%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20market%20investigation%20showed%20that%20despite%20not%20meeting%20the%20thresholds%2C%20iPadOS%20constitutes%20an%20important%20gateway%20on%20which%20many%20companies%20rely%20to%20reach%20their%20customers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20condition%20under%20the%20DMA%20is%20that%20companies%20are%20barred%20from%20self-preferencing.%20This%20means%20that%20Apple%20legally%20can't%20favor%20its%20own%20products%20and%20services%20over%20its%20competitors%20through%20its%20platforms.%20Instead%2C%20firms%20such%20as%20Apple%20must%20let%20app%20developers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-app-store-shakeup-in-europe-triggers-fury-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bsteer%26quot%3B%20consumers%20to%20offers%20outside%20its%20own%20App%20Store%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20commission%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-slapped-with-whopping-fine-of-nearly-2-billion-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehit%20Apple%20with%20a%20fine%20of%20nearly%20%242%20billion%20%3C%2Fa%3Eafter%20it%20found%20the%20firm%20had%20restricted%20app%20developers%20from%20informing%20users%20about%20other%2C%20cheaper%20music%20services.%20Apple%20said%20it%20would%20appeal%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-eu-commission-ipad-system-named-gatekeeper-clampdown-digital-dominance-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714393344000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662f87fc10dfcda409644bad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-eu-commission-ipad-system-named-gatekeeper-clampdown-digital-dominance-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20European%20Commission%20has%20put%20Apple%20on%20notice%20and%20given%20it%20six%20months%20to%20ensure%20its%20iPadOS%20complies%20with%20the%20Digital%20Markets%20Act.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jmann%40insider.com%20(Jyoti%20Mann)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-eu-commission-ipad-system-name