alUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Feducation-ministry-calls-for-annual-review-and-update-of-ncert-textbooks-5549899%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Feducation-ministry-calls-for-annual-review-and-update-of-ncert-textbooks-5549899%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Feducation-ministry-calls-for-annual-review-and-update-of-ncert-textbooks-5549899%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%223%20women%20contracted%20HIV%20after%20getting%20'vampire%20facials'%20at%20an%20unlicensed%20medical%20spa%2C%20federal%20authorities%20say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20doctor%20and%20a%20Botox%20injection%20at%20a%20walk-in%20Botox%20salon%20in%20New%20York%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662f869310dfcda409644b74%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20doctor%20preparing%20a%20Botox%20injection%20at%20a%20walk-in%20salon%20in%20New%20York%20on%20July%2017%2C%202007.%3Cp%3EReuters%2FLucas%20Jackson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThree%20women%20contracted%20HIV%20after%20getting%C2%A0%26quot%3Bvampire%20facial%26quot%3B%20procedures%20at%20an%20unlicensed%20medical%20spa.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20CDC%20said%20these%20were%20the%20first%20known%20cases%20of%20people%20getting%20the%20virus%20this%20way.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20investigation%20found%20that%20the%20spa%20in%20New%20Mexico%20reused%20disposable%20electric%20desiccator%20tips.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20women%20contracted%20HIV%20after%20getting%20%26quot%3Bvampire%20facial%26quot%3B%20procedures%20at%20an%20unlicensed%20medical%20spa%20in%20New%20Mexico%2C%20according%20to%20federal%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%20said%20in%20its%20latest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fmmwr%2Fvolumes%2F73%2Fwr%2Fmm7316a3.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMorbidity%20and%20Mortality%20Weekly%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20released%20last%20week%2C%20that%20the%20three%20patients%20were%20the%20first%20documented%20cases%20of%20people%20contracting%20the%20virus%20through%20cosmetic%20injection%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CDC%20said%20it%20started%20an%20investigation%20in%202018%20after%20the%20New%20Mexico%20Department%20of%20Health%20found%20a%20positive%20HIV%20test%20from%20a%20woman%20in%20her%2040s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20the%20patient%20reported%20no%20injection%20drug%20use%2C%20recent%20blood%20transfusions%2C%20or%20recent%20sexual%20contact%20with%20anyone%20other%20than%20her%20current%20sexual%20partner%2C%20per%20the%20National%20Public%20Health%20Agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20did%20report%20exposure%20to%20needles%20during%20a%20micro-needling%20procedure%20at%20a%20spa%20in%20Albuquerque%2C%20New%20Mexico%2C%20per%20the%20CDC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20procedure%2C%20aimed%20at%20making%20the%20skin%20look%20smoother%2C%20tighter%2C%20and%20fuller%2C%20involves%20collecting%20blood%20from%20a%20patient%2C%20separating%20the%20plasma%20and%20platelets%2C%20and%20re-injecting%20the%20mixture%20into%20the%20skin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20involves%20many%20small%20punctures%20across%20the%20forehead%20and%20cheeks%2C%20or%20injecting%20the%20blood%20into%20the%20skin%20like%20filler%2C%20a%20procedure%20known%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bvampire%20facelift.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFacials%20of%20this%20kind%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-vampire-facials-2017-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epopular%20among%20celebrities%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20Kim%20Kardashian%20and%20Bar%20Refaeli%2C%20and%20cost%20about%20%241%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20found%20that%20four%20clients%20of%20the%20spa%20and%20one%20sexual