y%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Mark%20Herlting%2C%20a%20former%20US%20lieutenant%20general%2C%20said%20Ukraine%20still%20faces%20serious%20obstacles%20in%20its%20bid%20to%20win%20back%20territory%20seized%20by%20Russia%2C%20with%20a%20shortage%20of%20recruits%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUkraine%20needs%20the%20mobilization%20of%20more%20soldiers.%20They%20have%20been%20on%20the%20battlefield%20for%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%2C%20and%20that%20just%20takes%20an%20incredible%20account%20of%20fatigue%2C%20psychological%20damage%2C%20and%20the%20toughness%20of%20being%20in%20the%20trenches%20in%20the%20front%20lines%20will%20really%20be%20a%20morale%20factor%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hertling%2C%20a%20former%20commander%20of%20US%20Army%20forces%20in%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%20long%20faced%20problems%20recruiting%20enough%20troops%20to%20renew%20its%20military%2C%20exhausted%20and%20badly%20depleted%20after%20more%20than%20two%20years%20of%20brutal%20war%20with%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fukraines-zelenskiy-signs-new-army-draft-law-reinforce-exhausted-troops-2024-04-16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Eunits%20on%20the%20front%20line%20are%20seriously%20overstretched%2C%20and%20troops%20have%20to%20fight%20for%20weeks%20in%20some%20cases%20before%20they%20are%20rotated%20away%20from%20the%20front%20line%20to%20recuperate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20forces%20have%20also%20been%20experiencing%20serious%20artillery%20and%20ammunition%20shortages%2C%20but%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20US%20aid%20bill%20after%20months%20of%20delays%20is%20expected%20to%20alleviate%20these%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHertling%20doesn't%20think%20weapons%20alone%20will%20allow%20Ukraine%20to%20regain%20the%20territories%20it%20has%20lost.%20%26quot%3BTruthfully%2C%20and%20I%20know%20some%20of%20my%20artillery%20brethren%20would%20chide%20me%20for%20this%2C%20but%20artillery%20and%20long-range%20systems%20do%20not%20win%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20take%20on%20and%20gain%20the%20terrain.%20Ukraine%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20do%20that%20to%20the%20extent%20they%20need%20to%20with%20some%20of%20the%20terrains%20they've%20lost%20to%20Russia.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recruitment%20issue%20has%20long%20been%20divisive%20in%20Ukraine.%20The%20country's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-army-chief-zaluzhnyi-russia-declining-support-west-win-technology-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eformer%20supreme%20military%20commander%2C%20Valerii%20Zaluzhnyi%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Eclashed%20with%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20over%20it%2C%20saying%20last%20year%20that%20Ukraine%20needed%20500%2C000%20more%20recruits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20government%20recently%20lowered%20the%20age%20at%20which%20people%20can%20be%20drafted%20into%20the%20military%20from%2027%20to%2025%2C%20but%20analysts%20believe%20it%20could%20be%20months%20before%20new%20recruits%20begin%20to%20make%20a%20difference%20on%20the%20front%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20also%20suffered%20steep%20losses%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20but%20it%20has%20a%20much%20larger%20population%20and%20has%20managed%20to%20boost%20the%20size%20of%20its%20military%20through%20drafts%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-recruiting-30000-troops-a-month-ukraine-frontline-losses-analysts-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eby%20offering%20recruits%20relatively%20lucrative%20contracts.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHertling%20said%20that%20new%20US%20weapons%20would%20help%20Ukraine%20resist%20Russian%20attacks%2C%20but%20it%20could%20be%20some%20time%20before%20they%20are%20in%20a%20position%20to%20take%20the%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20we're%20going%20to%20see%20the%20front%20stabilize%20a%20little%20bit%20over%20the%20next%20several%20weeks%2C%20and%20then%20potentially%20if%20Ukraine%20can%20not%20only%20get%20them%2C%20mobilized%2C%20soldiers%2C%20get%20them%20trained%2C%20get%20them%20into%20offensive%20operations%2C%20and%20get%20them%20into%20the%20ability%20to%20retake%20ground.%20That's%20what%20I'm%20looking%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20Hertling%20told%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-needs-troops-russia-war-artillery-says-ex-us-general-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714392037000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662f6ccaec0c696569fe8ca8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-needs-troops-russia-war-artillery-says-ex-us-general-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BUkraine%20needs%20the%20mobilisation%20of%20more%20soldiers%2C%26quot%3B%20Mark%20Hertling%20told%20CNN.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tporter%40businessinsider.com%20(Tom%20Porter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-needs-troops-russia-war-artillery-says-ex-us-general-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CSK%20make%20history%20with%20a%20massive%20world%20record%20for%20most...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714391917000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109695991%2Cimgsize-60196.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Fchennai-super-kings-make-history-with-massive-world-record-for-most-%2Farticleshow%2F109695950.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chennai%20Super%20Kings%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20successful%20teams%20in%20the%20IPL%2C%20have%20left%20an%20indelible%20mark%20on%20T20%20cricket%20history%20by%20achieving%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20200-plus%20totals%20in%20this%20short%20format%2