%20recording%20of%20his%20statement%20as%20required%20by%20the%20anti-money%20laundering%20law%2C%20said%20senior%20advocate%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPower%20to%20arrest%20is%20not%20the%20same%20as%20a%20need%20to%20arrest.%20Guilt%20has%20to%20be%20made%20out%2C%20not%20mere%20suspicion...%20This%20is%20also%20the%20threshold%20in%20Section%2045%20PMLA%20(Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20has%20challenged%20his%20arrest%20in%20the%20top%20court%20and%20filed%20an%20application%20for%20interim%20release%2C%20arguing%20that%20the%20arrest%20being%20illegal%2C%20his%20subsequent%20placement%20in%20custody%20is%20also%20unlawful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20why%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20has%20not%20filed%20a%20petition%20for%20bail%20in%20the%20trial%20court%2C%20Mr%20Singhvi%20told%20the%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Dipankar%20Datta%20that%20they%20have%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20because%20it%20has%20%26quot%3Bwider%20jurisdiction%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20had%20arrested%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20on%20March%2021%20after%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20refused%20to%20grant%20him%20protection.%20The%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20currently%20lodged%20in%20the%20Tihar%20jail.%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20has%20argued%20that%20the%20court's%20refusal%20to%20grant%20protection%20cannot%20be%20ground%20for%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20denial%20in%20interim%20of%20my%20bail%20cannot%20be%20ground%20to%20come%20to%20my%20home%20for%20arrest.%20The%20arrest%20did%20not%20happen%20for%201.5%20years.%20They%20arrested%20me%20from%20my%20home.%20They%20did%20not%20record%20Section%2050%20statement%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20counsel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20affidavit%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20has%20condemned%20his%20arrest%20as%20politically%20motivated%2C%20arguing%20that%20was%20meant%20to%20provide%20unfair%20advantages%20the%20ruling%20party%20during%20the%20ongoing%20general%20election.%20The%20case%2C%20he%20has%20argued%2C%20is%20a%20prime%20example%20of%20the%20Central%20government's%20misuse%20of%20investigative%20agencies%20to%20harass%20political%20opponents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20has%20argued%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%20became%20necessary%20due%20to%20his%20%26quot%3Btotal%20non-co-operative%20attitude%26quot%3B.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20affidavit%20said%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20was%20avoiding%20interrogation%20by%20not%20remaining%20present%20before%20the%20investigating%20officer%20despite%20being%20summoned%20nine%20times%20and%20while%20recording%20his%20statement%20under%20Section%2017%20of%20the%20PMLA%2C%20he%20was%20evasive%20and%20uncooperative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hearing%20will%20continue%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714389840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fhb1ndiok_arvind-kejriwal-pti_625x300_12_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-tells-supreme-court-why-he-filed-no-bail-petition-5549397%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%20is%20illegal%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20told%20today%20by%20the%20counsel%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-tells-supreme-court-why-he-filed-no-bail-petition-5549397%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-tells-supreme-court-why-he-filed-no-bail-petition-5549397%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-tells-supreme-court-why-he-filed-no-bail-petition-5549397%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NTPC%20Group's%20installed%20power%20generation%20capacity%20crosses%2076%20GW%20milestone