C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecut%20down%20on%20UPFs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20how%20many%20you're%20eating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20growing%20research%20suggests%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fultra-processed-foods-health-problems-study-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeating%20a%20diet%20high%20in%20UPFs%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20lead%20to%20potential%20health%20problems%20such%20as%20cardiovascular%20disease%2C%20type%202%20diabetes%2C%20obesity%2C%20and%20certain%20types%20of%20cancer%2C%20experts%20recommend%20people%20try%20to%20minimize%20their%20intake%20without%20fixating%20on%20eliminating%20them%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we're%20getting%20too%20bogged%20down%20with%20the%20term%20ultra-processed%20food%2C%20we%20just%20need%20to%20make%20it%20a%20bit%20simpler%2C%26quot%3B%20Patel%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThink%20about%20overall%20dietary%20patterns%20rather%20than%20the%20one-off%20treats%20we%20all%20indulge%20in%2C%20she%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3B70%2C%2080%25%20I'm%20eating%20whole%20food%2C%20but%2020%25%20I%20honestly%20do%20not%20care%20what%20I%20eat%2C%20and%20I%20grab%20whatever%20I%20want%20and%20fast.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1)%20How%20much%20of%20your%20diet%20is%20ultra-processed%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOfficial%20bodies%20like%20the%20FDA%20provide%20basic%20nutritional%20guidelines%2C%20and%20seeing%20how%20your%20diet%20compares%20is%20a%20good%20place%20to%20start%2C%20Patel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20we%20should%20be%20eating%20at%20least%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5-fiber-mistakes-how-to-fix-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E28%20grams%20of%20fiber%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20no%20more%20than%2050g%20of%20added%20sugar%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20UPFs%20are%20low%20in%20fiber%20and%20high%20in%20sugar%2C%20fat%2C%20and%20salt%20because%20they're%20ultra-palatable%2C%20meaning%20they%20contain%20the%20perfect%20combination%20of%20ingredients%20to%20make%20them%20irresistible%20and%20moreish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20very%20important%20to%20look%20at%20food%20labels%2C%20Patel%20said%2C%20so%20that%20you%20actually%20know%20what%20you're%20eating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUPFs%20come%20in%20all%20shapes%20and%20sizes%2C%20and%20some%20are%20certainly%20more%20nutrient-dense%20than%20others%2C%20she%20said.%20Even%20the%20same%20product%20made%20by%20a%20different%20manufacturer%20could%20contain%20more%20additives%20than%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Burger%20with%20American%20cheese%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662f7f72ec0c696569fe8edb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUltra-processed%20foods%20make%20up%2073%25%20of%20the%20US%20food%20supply.%3Cp%3EAleksandr%20Zubkov%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E2)%20Are%20you%20snacking%20smart%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20are%20a%20big%20snacker%2C%20it's%20worth%20taking%20a%20closer%20look%20at%20what%20you%20tend%20to%20eat%2C%20as%20items%20such%20as%20potato%20chips%20and%20cookies%20tend%20to%20be%20ultra-processed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20are%20really%20bad%20at%20doing%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20in%20the%20USA%20is%20eating%20on%20the%20go%2C%20and%20that%20means%20that%20those%20eating-on-the-go%20moments%20are%20where%20we%20reach%20out%20for%20ultra-processed%20food%2C%26quot%3B%20Patel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20sees%20this%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20reduce%20UPF%20consumption%20by%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fminimally-processed-grocery-store-snacks-nutritionist-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esnacking%20smarter%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIt%20could%20be%20an%20apple%20with%20a%20handful%20of%20nuts.%20That's%20something%20easy%20and%20portable%20that%20is%20going%20to%20be%20nutritious%20and%20balanced%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20really%20need%20your%20chocolate%20fix%2C%20you%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-eat-junk-food-without-binging-using-diet-hack-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeat%20a%20piece%20of%20fruit%20and%20then%20have%20some%20chocolate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20will%20probably%20mean%20you%20eat%20less%20of%20the%20processed%20snack%20overall%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E3)%20How%20well%20do%20you%20know%20yourself%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiet-culture-cycle-nutritionist-mindset-shift-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebehavior%20change%3C%2Fa%3E%20involved%20here%2C%20the%20same%20as%20any%20new%20habit%2C%20Patel%20said.%20So%20it's%20helpful%20to%20understand%20what%20works%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20like%20to%20dive%20into%20the%20deep%20end%20and%20might%20find%20going%20cold%20turkey%20a%20great%20approach.%20But%20for%20others%2C%20making%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-lost-105-pounds-walking-healthy-diet-wegovy-easier-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmall%2C%20incremental%20changes%3C%2Fa%3E%20might%20be%20better%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStart%20with%20something%20that%20you%20feel%20is%20doable%20and%20manageable%2C%20and%20then%20you%20build%20on%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20You%20might%20identify%20that%20most%20of%20your%20UPFs%20are%20coming%20from%20snacks%2C%20so%20you%20start%20there.%20Then%20with%20time%2C%20you%20target%20breakfast%2C%20and%20later%20lunch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwant-to-cut-down-on-upfs-3-questions-to-ask-yourself-dietitian-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714389094000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662a3b2523b29110d302d59f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwant-to-cut-down-on-upfs-3-questions-to-ask-yourself-dietitian-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Growing%20research%20is%20linking%20ultra-processed%20foods%20to%20poor%20health.%20A%20dietitian%20shared%20three%20questions%20to%20make%20cutting%20down%20on%20UFPs%20less%20overwhelming.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kschewitz%40businessinsider.com%20(Kim%20Schewitz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwant-to-cut-down-on-upfs-3-questions-to-ask-yourself-dietitian-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BSE%20Shares%20Tank%2019%25%20After%20SEBI's%20New%20Directive%20On%20Regulatory%20Fee%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELeading%20stock%20exchange%20BSE%20is%20expected%20to%20shell%20out%20more%20regulatory%20fee%20after%20the%20markets%20watchdog%20Sebi%20asked%20the%20bourse%20to%20pay%20the%20fee%20based%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bnotional%20value%26quot%3B%20of%20its%20options%20contracts%20rather%20than%20on%20the%20premium%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20development%2C%20shares%20of%20BSE%20have%20slumped%20as%20much%20as%2018.64%20per%20cent%20to%20an%20intra-day%20low%20of%20Rs%202%2C612.0%20on%20the%20NSE%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarket%20experts%20expect%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20BSE's%20regulatory%20fee%20payments%20to%20Sebi%20due%20to%20the%20significant%20variance%20between%20the%20notional%20and%20premium%20values.%20This%20discrepancy%20arises%20from%20the%20calculation%20method%2C%20which%20involves%20multiplying%20the%20contract%20size%20by%20the%20underlying%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotional%20turnover%20represents%20the%20overall%20strike%20price%20of%20all%20contracts%20traded%20in%20derivatives%2C%20whereas%20premium%20turnover%20is%20the%20sum%20of%20premiums%20paid%20on%20all%20contracts%20traded.%20As%20the%20notional%20value%20exceeds%20the%20premium%20turnover%2C%20opting%20for%20notional%20turnover%20as%20the%20basis%20entails%20a%20higher%20fee%20outlay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBSE%20is%20hereby%20advised%20to%20pay%20the%20regulatory%20fee%20based%20on%20annual%20turnover%20to%20Sebi%20considering%20the%20notional%20value%20in%20case%20of%20options%20contract%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20exchange%20said%20in%20a%20filing%20to%20the%20National%20Stock%20Exchange%20(NSE)%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20the%20exchange%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20pay%20the%20differential%20regulatory%20fee%20for%20the%20past%20periods%20along%20with%20an%20interest%20of%2015%20per%20cent%20per%20annum%20on%20the%20remaining%20unpaid%20amount.%20It%20has%20been%20directed%20to%20pay%20the%20amount%20within%20one%20month%20of%20the%20receipt%20of%20the%20letter%2C%20the%20filing%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESebi's%20letter%20mentioned%20that%20since%20the%20introduction%20of%20derivative%20contracts%2C%20BSE%20has%20been%20paying%20the%20regulatory%20fee%20on%20%26quot%3Bannual%20turnover%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20regulator%20considering%20premium%20value%20for%20option%20contracts%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20notional%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20disclosure%20on%20Sunday%2C%20BSE%20said%20it%20is%20currently%20evaluating%20the%20validity%20of%20the%20claim%20as%20per%20Sebi%20communication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20case%20it%20is%20ascertained%20that%20the%20said%20amount%20is%20payable%2C%20the%20total%20differential%20Sebi%20regulatory%20fees%20for%20the%20period%20from%20FY%202006-07%20to%20FY%202022-23%20would%20be%20Rs%2068.64%20crore%20plus%20GST%2C%20which%20includes%20an%20interest%20of%20Rs%2030.34%20crore.%20Further%2C%20the%20differential%20Sebi%20regulatory%20fees%20for%20FY%202023-24%2C%20if%20liable%2C%20could%20be%20around%20Rs%2096.30%20crore%20plus%20GST%2C%20BSE%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20markets%20watchdog%20had%20in