%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20his%20disappointing%20run%20of%20form%20has%20resulted%20in%20major%20questions%20over%20his%20possible%20inclusion%20for%20the%20upcoming%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024.%20Hardik%20dominated%20headlines%20ahead%20of%20the%20IPL%202024%20season%20as%20he%20completed%20a%20sensational%20trade%20from%20Gujarat%20Titans%20and%20Mumbai%20Indians.%20Things%20heated%20up%20even%20more%20when%20he%20ended%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E's%20ten-year%20tenure%20as%20MI%20captain%20-%20a%20decision%20that%20was%20not%20taken%20well%20by%20a%20section%20of%20their%20fanbase.%20Questions%20over%20Hardik's%20leadership%2C%20rumours%20of%20a%20rift%20with%20Rohit%20and%20speculations%20over%20how%20other%20players%20will%20react%20to%20the%20decision%20became%20prime%20fodder%20for%20media%20reports%20following%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20got%20worse%20as%20MI%20slumped%20to%20three%20defeats%20on%20the%20trot%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20competition%20and%20the%20skipper%20was%20booed%20by%20a%20part%20of%20the%20crowd%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20in%20Mumbai.%20The%20five-time%20champions%20did%20find%20some%20form%20in%20the%20competition%20but%20it%20was%20not%20enough%20as%20they%20are%20currently%20languishing%20in%20ninth%20position%20in%20the%20IPL%202024%20points%20table%20with%20just%206%20points%20from%209%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHardik's%20performance%20as%20a%20player%20has%20also%20left%20a%20lot%20to%20be%20desired%20for%20the%20MI%20fans%20as%20he%20scored%20just%20197%20runs%20in%209%20matches%20and%20with%20the%20ball%2C%20he%20took%204%20wickets%20at%20an%20exorbitant%20economy%20rate%20of%C2%A011.95.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20squad%20announcement%2C%20NDTV%20Sports%20conducted%20a%20poll%20to%20see%20what%20the%20fans%20think.%20According%20to%20the%20poll%2C%20which%20was%20conducted%20on%20%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwhatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029VaBMbml6WaKl7Q12Fc2i%5C%22%3ENDTV%20Cricket's%20WhatsApp%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20fans%C2%A0%20think%20that%20Hardik%20should%20not%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20for%20the%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20a%20look%20at%20the%20poll%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F1bc2r68o_f_625x300_29_April_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D806%2Cheight%3D605%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20numbers%20may%20not%20be%20in%20Hardik's%20favour%2C%20the%20TINA%20(There%20Is%20No%20Alternative)%20factor%20continue%20to%20keep%20him%20in%20contention.%20A%20medium%20pacer%20all-rounder%20is%20a%20rare%20commodity%20for%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20and%20considering%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20are%20no%20other%20choices%2C%20the%20selectors%20may%20end%20up%20choosing%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20it%20looks%20like%20the%20selectors%20will%20go%20with%20three%20specialist%20fast%20bowlers%20and%20with%20other%20all-rounders%20like%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravindra%20Jadeja%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F855-ravindra-jadeja-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavindra%20Jadeja%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Axar%20Patel%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F63024-akshar-rajeshbhai-patel-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAxar%20Patel%3C%2Fa%3E%20providing%20only%20spin%20options%2C%20Hardik%20can%20end%20up%20getting%20selected%20as%20the%20