still%26quot%3B%20After%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Arrest%3A%20High%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20has%20%26quot%3Bcome%20to%20a%20standstill%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20arrest%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20the%20High%20Court%20said%20today%20while%20hearing%20a%20petition%20on%20the%20state%20of%20education%20in%20schools%20run%20by%20the%20city%20civic%20body.%20A%20Chief%20Minster's%20post%20in%20a%20buzzing%20capital%20like%20Delhi%20is%20not%20ceremonial%20and%20it%20is%20post%20where%20the%20office%20holder%20has%20to%20be%20available%2024x7.%20His%20absence%20cannot%20deprive%20children%20of%20their%20free%20text%20books%2C%20writing%20material%20and%20uniforms%2C%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNational%20interest%20and%20public%20interest%20demands%20that%20no%20person%20who%20holds%20this%20post%20is%20incommunicado%20or%20absent%20for%20a%20long%20stretch%20or%20for%20an%20uncertain%20period%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20bench%20of%20Acting%20Chief%20Justice%20Manmohan%20and%20Justice%20Manmeet%20Pritam%20Singh%20Arora.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20held%20that%20the%20admission%20of%20Delhi's%C2%A0Urban%20Development%20Minister%20Saurabh%20Bhardwaj%20--%20that%20any%20increase%20in%20financial%20power%20of%20MCD%20commissioner%20shall%20require%20approval%20of%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20-%20amounts%20to%20an%20admission%20that%20%26quot%3BDelhi%20government%20has%20come%20to%20a%20standstill%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20had%20maintained%20that%20nearly%20two%20lakh%20students%20lacked%20basic%20amenities%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20academic%20year%20due%20to%20administrative%20hurdles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%20on%20April%2026%2C%20the%20High%20Court%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20the%20Delhi%20government%20and%20the%20civic%20body%20for%20their%20failure%20to%20provide%20textbooks.%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20insistence%20on%20holding%20the%20post%20even%20after%20his%20arrest%20in%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case%20puts%20political%20interest%20over%20national%20interest%2C%20the%20judges%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20rebuke%2C%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20had%20accused%20the%20AAP-led%20Delhi%20government%20and%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20of%20delaying%20the%20approval%20of%20a%20proposal%20to%20temporarily%20enhance%20the%20financial%20powers%20of%20the%20MCD%20Commissioner%20from%20Rs%205%20crore%20to%20Rs%2050%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20argued%20that%20the%20delay%20has%20hampered%20some%20crucial%20projects%20linked%20to%20education%2C%20health%2C%20and%20sanitation%2C%20as%20the%20Standing%20Committee%20of%20the%20Corporation%20has%20not%20been%20constituted%20for%20over%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714386900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fkacr7vh_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_27_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgovernment-at-a-standstill-after-arvind-kejriwal-arrest-high-court-5548940%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20government%20has%20come%20to%20a%20standstill%20after%20the%20arrest%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20the%20High%20Court%20said%20today%20while%20hearing%20a%20petition%20on%20the%20state%20of%20education%20in%20schools%20run%20by%20the%20city%20civic%20body.%20A%20Chief%20Minster's%20post%20in%20a%20buzzing%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgovernment-at-a-standstill-after-arvind-kejriwal-arrest-high-court-5548940%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgovernment-at-a-standstill-after-arvind-kejriwal-arrest-high-court-5548940%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgovern