e%20family%2C%20friends%2C%20volunteers%20and%20strangers%20who%20called%20in%20tips%20and%20made%20this%20recovery%20possible.%20We%20especially%20want%20to%20thank%20the%20seasoned%20law%20enforcement%20officers%20who%20understand%20the%20very%20real%20threat%20of%20predators%20who%20use%20the%20allure%20of%20drugs%20to%20groom%20teenagers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20family%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMint%20was%20reported%20missing%20after%20%26quot%3Brunning%20away%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20family's%20Marin%20County%20residence.%20They%20were%20last%20seen%20near%20her%20home%20on%20Sunday%2C%20April%2021%20at%20approximately%2010%20pm%20in%20Bolinas%2C%20California.%20The%20teen%20was%20reported%20missing%20on%20Monday%20at%208%3A30%20am%20by%20the%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tenderloin%20neighbourhood%20is%20known%20for%20its%20high%20crime%20rate%20and%20is%20home%20to%20a%20sizable%20portion%20of%20the%20city's%20homeless%20population.%20It%20has%20lately%20become%20well-known%20for%20being%20the%20epicentre%20of%20the%20fentanyl%20issue%20in%20California%2C%20which%20is%20a%20subset%20of%20the%20larger%20opioid%20crisis%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20Metro.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Flickr%20was%20founded%20in%202004%20by%20Caterina%20Fake%20and%20Stewart%20Butterfield%2C%20who%20used%20a%20tool%20they%20had%20developed%20for%20an%20online%20game%20to%20establish%20the%20platform.%20They%20divorced%20in%202007.%20Mr%20Butterfield%20then%20established%20the%20communication%20platform%20Slack%20in%202012.%20Now%2C%20with%20over%2010%20million%20daily%20active%20users%2C%20Slack%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20vital%20tool%20in%20offices%20all%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714386840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fps9a9v18_mint-butterfield_625x300_25_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fslack-co-founders-missing-teen-found-26-ye