nna-radiates-regal-vibes-in-heavily-embroidered-mint-green-anarkali%2Fphotostory%2F109656764.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109656764.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERashmika%20Mandanna's%20anarkali%20is%20perfect%20for%20a%20friend's%20wedding.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Upset%20Congress%20Workers'%20%26quot%3BTold%20You%20So%26quot%3B%20After%20Indore%20Candidate%20Joins%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20abrupt%20exit%20of%20the%20Congress's%20Indore%20candidate%20Akshay%20Kanti%20Bam%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20has%20left%20the%20party%20wondering%20why%20he%20took%20that%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bam%20withdrew%20his%20nomination%20papers%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20word%20on%20the%20Congress%20street%20is%20that%20party%20workers%20are%20upset%20the%20leadership%20did%20not%20consider%20their%20request%20not%20to%20field%20somebody%20%26quot%3Bunreliable%26quot%3B%20as%20Mr%20Bam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20visibly%20upset%20Congress%20worker%20told%20reporters%20he%20had%20in%20a%20meeting%20with%20senior%20leaders%20of%20the%20party%20warned%20them%20that%20Mr%20Ban%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20person%20who%20will%20withdraw%20his%20candidature%20later%2C%20under%20pressure%20from%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20warned%20them%20right%20from%20the%20start%2C%20indicated%20to%20our%20leaders%2C%20do%20not%20give%20a%20ticket%20to%20Akshay%20Bam.%20Give%20to%20a%20loyal%20party%20worker%2C%20somebody%20like%20me.%20I'd%20fight%20the%20election%20with%20all%20my%20might%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20party%20worker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20told%20them%20not%20to%20give%20ticket%20to%20a%20candidate%20with%20money%20as%20Akshay%20Bam.%20They%20should%20realise%20the%20wealth%20of%20Congress%20is%20their%20party%20workers.%20I%20knew%20Akshay%20Bam%20would%20withdraw%20his%20name%20because%20BJP%20gives%20tickets%20to%20people%20who%20have%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20told%20all%20this%20at%20the%20Congress%20office%20where%20Sajjan%20Verma%20ji%2C%20Surjit%20Chaddha%2C%20and%20Ravi%20Joshi%20ji%20and%20many%20others%20were%20present...%20Now%20the%20Congress%20will%20have%20to%20pay%20the%20price%20for%20ignoring%20party%20workers.%20The%20party%20should%20give%20tickets%20to%20party%20workers%20who%20have%20been%20with%20the%20party%20for%20years%20and%20years.%20If%20the%20party%20doesn't%20trust%20us%2C%20the%20Congress%20will%20lose%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%20minister%20Kailash%20Vijayvargiya%20later%20posted%20a%20picture%20with%20Mr%20Bam%20on%20X%2C%20welcoming%20him%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20BJP%20nominee%20from%20Vidisha%20seat%2C%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%2C%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20Congress%20saying%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20party%20has%20become%20such%20that%20even%20candidates%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20within%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFaith%20of%20all%20the%20leaders%20and%20workers%20is%20in%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20BJP.%20The%20condition%20of%20the%20Congress%20has%20become%20such%20that%20even%20candidates%20do%20not%20want%20to%20be%20within%20its%20party.%20Today%2C%20a%20Congress%20candidate%20from%20Indore%20Lok%20Sabha%20joined%20the%20BJP.%20Now%2C%20this%20is%20the%20Congress%20whose%20candidate%20does%20not%20have%20faith%20in%20the%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chouhan%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20of%20Indore%20will%20vote%20in%20the%20fourth%20phase%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20on%20May%2013%2C%20with%20seven%20other%20parliamentary%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20are%20being%20conducted%20in%20four%20phases.%20Votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20June%204.%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20has%20a%20total%20of%2029%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituencies%2C%20making%20it%20the%20sixth-largest%20state%20in%20terms%20of%20parliamentary%20representation.%20Out%20of%20these%2C%2010%20seats%20are%20reserved%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20while%20the%20remaining%2019%20are%20unreserved.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714386480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fhkqrug2o_congress-worker_625x300_29_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-upset-congress-workers-told-you-so-after-indore-candidate-akshay-kanti-bam-joins-bjp-5548934%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20abrupt%20exit%20of%20the%20Congress's%20Indore%20candidate%20Akshay%20Kanti%20Bam%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20has%20left%20the%20party%20wondering%20why%20he%20took%20that%20step.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-upset-congress-workers-told-you-so-after-indore-candidate-akshay-kanti-bam-joins-bjp-5548934%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-upset-congress-workers-told-you-so-after-indore-candidate-akshay-kanti-bam-joins-bjp-5548934%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-upset-congress-workers-told-you-so-after-indore-candidate-akshay-kanti-bam-joins-bjp-5548934%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Spanish%20PM%20decides%20not%20to%20quit%20despite%20corruption%20claims%20against%20wife%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714386480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F04%2F1920x108