22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Where%20Did%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20Love%20Affair%20with%20Dosa%20Originate%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20motivation%20for%20me%20to%20wake%20up%20early%20on%20a%20Sunday%20morning%20is%20to%20eat%20my%20favourite%20%3Cem%3Ebutter%20masala%20dose%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20%3Cem%3Edosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%20filtered%20coffee.%20The%20joint%20near%20my%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347615%2Fbengaluru-water-crisis-measures-to-save-water-at-home-greywater-rainwater-odette-katrak-designs-ecowaternomics-framework%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehome%20in%20Bengaluru%20%3C%2Fa%3Eserves%20the%20most%20crispy%20and%20buttery%20%3Cem%3Edosas%3C%2Fem%3E%20ever!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20love%20affair%20with%20the%20dish%20is%20common%20to%20most%20Bengaluru%20residents.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20citizens%20of%20the%20garden%20city%20ordered%20a%20whopping%2029%20million%20%3Cem%3Edosas%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20with%20an%20average%20of%20122%20%3Cem%3Edosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20per%20minute%20just%20during%20breakfast%20hours!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20these%20sky-touching%20numbers%20make%20one%20think%20%E2%80%94%20how%20did%20this%20delicious%20dish%20come%20into%20existence%3F%20Well%2C%20we%20did%20some%20research%20and%20came%20across%20some%20amazing%20theories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20intriguing%20story%20comes%20from%20Udupi%20when%20a%20cook%20fermented%20some%20rice%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20make%20alcohol.%20Failing%20in%20doing%20so%2C%20he%20poured%20the%20fermented%20batter%20on%20a%20hot%20pan%20and%20voila%20%E2%80%94%20he%20accidentally%20gave%20the%20world%20its%20first%20%3Cem%3Edosa%3C%2Fem%3E!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20believe%20that%20the%20dish%20was%20concocted%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20in%20the%20first%20century.%20While%20others%20believe%20that%20the%20Chalukya%20King%20Someshvara%20III%20w